934
00:44:28.416 --> 00:44:29.583
thirty million dollars.

935
00:44:30.666 --> 00:44:32.083
Did she say
thirty million?

936
00:44:32.250 --> 00:44:35.125
So. we have our motive.

937
00:44:35.916 --> 00:44:37.625
