956
00:46:14.083 --> 00:46:15.875
There you go. Good boy.

957
00:46:16.041 --> 00:46:17.291
There you are.

958
00:46:20.583 --> 00:46:21.903
These sheep
will keep running amok

959
00:46:21.958 --> 00:46:23.875
