it wasn't the maid.

992
00:47:58.958 --> 00:48:00.041
No more maids!

993
00:48:00.166 --> 00:48:01.958
Ugh. sheep.

994
00:48:02.125 --> 00:48:05.750
Caleb will be our
new shepherd. won't he. Lily?

995
00:48:05.916 --> 00:48:06.916
Of course.

996
00:48:07.041 --> 00:48:09.666
We... We just need to wait
