997
00:48:09.833 --> 00:48:10.833
I have a question.

998
00:48:11.000 --> 00:48:12.791
Why haven't you solved
the mystery yet. Lily?

999
00:48:12.958 --> 00:48:13.833
You solve them

1000
00:48:13.958 --> 00:48:15.358
